@BadboyJay55 

No u must download them all.  Think of it like a puzzle thats not put together. So once its downloaded you open up the first rar and there will be a file in it.  Click and drag this file to your desktop or your download folder. Then a winrar box apears and it will show you the status of the files being put together. So winrar puts all the files together for you. Hope this helps.
